BT /F2 10 Tf 50 724 Td (- Phase 1: HTTPX and urllib.parse for fetching pages, handling redirects,) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 710 Td (headers, cookies, status codes, and URL normalization.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 694 Td (- Phase 2: Beautiful Soup for crawling links, forms, scripts, images, and page) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 680 Td (structure.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 664 Td (- Phase 3: ssl and socket for certificate expiry, TLS basics, and hostname) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 650 Td (verification.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 634 Td (- Phase 4: Pydantic for findings, scan results, and configuration models.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 618 Td (- Phase 5: Typer and Rich for a clean CLI with tables, progress bars, and) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 604 Td (severity labels.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 588 Td (- Phase 6: JSON and Jinja2 for machine-readable exports and HTML reports.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 572 Td (- Phase 7: pytest for regression coverage and confidence as the scanner grows.) Tj ET
BT /F1 13 Tf 50 556 Td (Practice Targets) Tj ET
