BT /F1 13 Tf 50 488 Td (What to Focus on First) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 468 Td (HTTP and HTTPS basics, security headers, cookies and session security, CORS, TLS) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 454 Td (and SSL basics, redirects, directory listing, exposed sensitive files, dangerous) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 440 Td (HTTP methods, server information disclosure, and WAF signals.) Tj ET
BT /F1 13 Tf 50 424 Td (What to Skip for v1) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 404 Td (Skip ML features, AI features, advanced exploitation, malware analysis,) Tj ET
